window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Scarred but Victorious.</b></p> <p>Adelheid returned to the capital of the Vuldar Empire after completing her Reginnaglar Ceremony. Armed with prestige and power, the seventh princess lays down the foundation for her rise. Although Adelheid has set her sights on the future, the past never escaped her eyes. Now, is the time for vengeance for both herself and her fallen knight.</p> <p><b>For Neun.</b></p>"; 
